  "subject": "Chore: Modernize docs configuration for Python 3.12+",
  "commit_message": "Chore: Modernize docs configuration for Python 3.12+\n\nRemove broken/outdated Python modules that are incompatible with modern\nPython versions. Replace lfdocs-conf dependency with standalone conf.py.\nUpdate .readthedocs.yaml to use ubuntu-24.04 and Python 3.13. Modernize\ntox.ini (use allowlist_externals, pin basepython to 3.12, add constraints).\nRemove obsolete docs/conf.yaml. Fix ribbon.css max-width per doc-rules.\nAdd etc/upper-constraints.onap.txt from the doc repo.\n\nRemoved modules: sphinxcontrib-swaggerdoc, sphinxcontrib-needs,\nsphinxcontrib-nwdiag, sphinx_bootstrap_theme, lfdocs-conf, doc8, six.\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nChange-Id: I26ae93957997a5dcea4eaf3dce7d3450fc501815\nSigned-off-by: Matthew Watkins <mwatkins@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
